<concept id="conceptId">
    <title>About Table Quick Search</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>In this type of search field, the following syntax is accepted:</p>
        <p><codeph>[&lt;column>(,&lt;column>)*:]&lt;expr>(;[&lt;column>(,&lt;column>)*:]&lt;expr>)*</codeph></p>
        <p>Possible elements:</p>
        <p>
            <ul id="ul_wht_lyg_bj">
                <li><codeph>&lt;column></codeph><p>The name of a column in the displayed
                    table.</p></li>
                <li>
                    <codeph>&lt;expr></codeph><p>Either a regular expression (regex), a phone
                        sequence expression (phonex) or plain text.</p></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>Some example expressions:
            <table frame="none" id="table_654bb29b-6724-4boe-b7f6-15470d928887">
                <title/>
                <tgroup cols="3">
                    <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                    <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3*"/>
                    <thead>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Expression</entry>
                            <entry>Matches</entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>b</entry>
                            <entry>Any row with a column that contains 'b'</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Speaker:Anne; b</entry>
                            <entry>Any row where column 'Speaker' is 'Anne' and any other column contains
                        'b'</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>IPA Target:b{v}</entry>
                            <entry>Any row where the IPA Target column contains 'b' followed by a
                        vowel</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>IPA Target,IPA Actual:k{v}</entry>
                            <entry>Any row where either the IPA Target or the IPA Actual column contains
                        'k' followed by a vowel</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Orthography:c; IPA Target:{c}{g}</entry>
                            <entry>Any row where the Orthography column contains 'c' and IPA Target
                        contains a consonant followed by a glide.</entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table></p>
    </conbody>
</concept>
